## `quote`

``` hol4
Lib.quote : string -> string
```

------------------------------------------------------------------------

Put quotation marks around a string.

An application `quote s` is equal to `"\"" ^ s ^ "\""`. This is often
useful when printing messages.

### Failure

Never fails

### Example

``` hol4
>> print "foo\n";

>> print (quote "foo" ^ "\n");
```

### See also

[`Lib.mlquote`](#Lib.mlquote)
